---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import RelatedPosts from "../components/RelatedPosts.astro";

const metaTitle = "Assistive Solutions: Essentials for Living Fully, Not Luxuries";
const metaDescription =
  "Why assistive solutions like swivel car seats, wheelchair ramps, and lifts are essential lifelines in India—not luxuries—providing safety, access, and independence.";
const currentSlug = "assistive-solutions-essentials-for-living-fully-not-luxuries";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/") ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
const ogImage = `${base}logo.png`;
---

<BaseLayout title={metaTitle} description={metaDescription} headerVariant="solid">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta property="og:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={ogImage} />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={ogImage} />
  </Fragment>

  <article class="article">
    <header class="article-head">
      <p class="article-date">October 14, 2025 · by Vandana</p>
      <h1>{metaTitle}</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-grid">
      <div class="article-body">
        <p>
          Too often, people see assistive solutions as “extras.” But the truth is, assistive technology in India is not about
          luxury—it’s about giving people equal access to everyday life.
        </p>

        <h2>Busting the Myth</h2>
        <p>
          For someone with mobility challenges, a handicap swivel car seat isn’t an accessory—it’s independence. For seniors,
          an aluminum wheelchair ramp is not a gadget—it’s the difference between isolation and participation.
        </p>

        <h2>What They Provide</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Rotating car seat India options make vehicle transfers safer.</li>
          <li>Wheelchair lifts ensure access to higher floors.</li>
          <li>Accessible living solutions like grab bars and ramps prevent accidents at home.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why It Matters</h2>
        <p>
          When society views disability aids for seniors as essentials, not luxuries, homes and public spaces become
          welcoming for all.
        </p>

        <h2>Final Thought</h2>
        <p>
          From aluminum wheelchair ramp to handicap swivel car seats, these are not luxuries but lifelines. Assistive
          solutions give people the power to live fully, not just survive.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar" aria-label="Products">
        <div class="products-card">
          <h2>Products</h2>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nlMO30_RrKc"
                title="TurnPlus video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus</p>
              <p class="product-link">Manual swivel seat for safer entry.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-electric" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ytQ7nRd8rf4"
                title="TurnPlus Electric video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus Electric</p>
              <p class="product-link">Powered swivel convenience.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-accelerate" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-bSUnSfkD-8"
                title="TurnPlus Accelerate video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus Accelerate</p>
              <p class="product-link">Rapid, smooth swivel assistance.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>

  <RelatedPosts currentSlug={currentSlug} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .article {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .article-head h1 {
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
    color: #451e5d;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .article-date {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .article-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .article-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }

  h2 {
    color: #451e5d;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.35rem;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }

  .sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 96px;
    align-self: start;
  }

  .products-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: #f9f9f9;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .products-card h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.6rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: #fff;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .product-card:hover,
  .product-card:focus-visible {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    outline: none;
  }

  .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: 56.25%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #000;
  }

  .video-frame iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  .product-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.1rem;
  }

  .product-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-link {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .article-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
